{
  "school_name": "Carleton University",
  "notes": [
    "Config-driven coverage of the student-relevant slice of carleton.ca.",
    "Fan-out is ONE hop from each hub URL (same-prefix links found on the hub page),",
    "so deep sections get their own sub-hub entry rather than relying on depth crawling.",
    "NOT here on purpose: 'dates' stays curated in calendar_feed.py (shared with the ICS",
    "feed and deadline tracker), 'facts' stays curated in scrape_facts.py, and 'schedule'",
    "stays on scrapers/active/ingest_schedule.py (Banner is form/session-driven, not",
    "crawlable). Library hours/study-room pages render via LibCal JavaScript widgets and",
    "will be thin until the LibCal source lands.",
    "Hub URL lists are ported from the proven legacy scrapers: scrape_registrar.py,",
    "scrape_regulations.py, scrape_programs.py, scrape_tuition.py, scrape_campus.py."
  ],
